reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 1, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Needs some improvements....
reviews.reviewText: As a water bottle holder, it’s great. My 40oz Stanley fits perfectly. The strap is adjustable and comfortable. Perfect for a walks, hiking, camping…. As far as the compartment for your phone and/or keys, not so great. When the water bottle is not in the pouch, it is big enough to fit an iPhone 13 Pro or Samsung S21 Ultra. There’s a mesh spot inside where your phone would go as well. The front part isn’t zippered, so I’d never put any credit cards or ID inside of there. Where it needs improvements….. There is not enough room for your phone and water bottle at the same time. The pouch for your phone needs to be wider, and the part for your credit cards should have a zipper.
